thread.title: Jacqueline Kelly

author: Jacqueline Kelly
title: Jacqueline Kelly
text: Overall Good service and experience from 25plus. I dont like that there is no phone number to contact the service. Difficult if you get a hire car and want to transfer your insurance immediately. Correspondence is through i message and request a call back. I would like a phone number to ring . When the staff ring back there are polite and explain all issues.
